<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:27:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国最新刺激措施未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</link><description>周五，投资者希望中国宣布为唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统的经济提供额外的财政缓冲，但他们感到失望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国就沃尔沃电动汽车关税协议进行谈判后，瑞典将目光转向布鲁塞尔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sweden-looks-brussels-after-china-talks-volvo-ev-tariff-deal-2024-11-08/</link><description>瑞典外交部长在结束对中国的访问时告诉路透社，瑞典希望欧盟和中国能够尽快就电动汽车达成定价协议，以试图限制进口关税争端对沃尔沃的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:48:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sweden-looks-brussels-after-china-talks-volvo-ev-tariff-deal-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>尽管金价高企，历峰集团仍对提高珠宝价格持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-remains-cautious-raising-jewellery-prices-despite-high-gold-prices-2024-11-08/</link><description>高管们周五表示，尽管近几个月金价飙升，卡地亚母公司历峰集团仍计划坚持谨慎提高珠宝价格，并且尚未有在未来几个月提价的计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-remains-cautious-raising-jewellery-prices-despite-high-gold-prices-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：大选后华尔街因美联储降息和中国刺激而繁荣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，台积电将从周一开始暂停为中国生产先进人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tsmc-suspend-production-advanced-ai-chips-china-monday-ft-reports-2024-11-08/</link><description>据《金融时报》周五援引三名知情人士的话报道，台积电已通知中国芯片设计公司，从周一开始暂停生产其先进的人工智能芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tsmc-suspend-production-advanced-ai-chips-china-monday-ft-reports-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>印度大米库存创历史新高，是政府目标的三倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-rice-inventories-hit-record-high-triples-govt-target-2024-11-08/</link><description>消息人士周五称，由于过去两年实施的出口限制增加了当地供应，印度11月份大米库存飙升至2970万吨的历史新高，几乎是政府目标的三倍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-rice-inventories-hit-record-high-triples-govt-target-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>分析师对中国提高地方政府债务上限的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国最高立法机构周五批准了一项法案，允许地方政府在三年内发行6万亿元人民币（合8,388亿美元）的债券，以置换表外或“隐性”债务，因为政策制定者试图刺激低迷的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>结交新朋友并增加招聘：中国芯片行业计划如何应对特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/make-new-friends-boost-hiring-how-chinas-chip-industry-plans-deal-with-trump-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国半导体行业正准备在唐纳德·特朗普担任美国总统期间迎接四年的激烈竞争，加大对外国芯片制造设备的采购力度，寻找聘用海外人才和建立新联盟的机会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:12:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/make-new-friends-boost-hiring-how-chinas-chip-industry-plans-deal-with-trump-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾被排除在气候峰会之外，设立“作战室”观看会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-excluded-climate-summit-sets-up-war-room-watch-talks-2024-11-08/</link><description>环境部长彭志明周五表示，鉴于台湾因政治原因不能参加，台湾已设立一个“作战室”来观看下周 COP29 气候峰会的直播。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:56:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-excluded-climate-summit-sets-up-war-room-watch-talks-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国钢铁制造商面临特朗普间接关税打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-steelmakers-gird-indirect-trump-tariffs-hit-2024-11-08/</link><description>如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品（例如由合金制成的制成品）征收60％的关税，已经在产能过剩和内需疲软中挣扎的中国钢铁业将面临间接打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:14:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-steelmakers-gird-indirect-trump-tariffs-hit-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>政府数据显示印度4月至9月钢铁进口量以中国为首</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-sept-steel-imports-led-by-china-govt-data-shows-2024-11-08/</link><description>路透社周五查阅的临时政府数据显示，印度 4 月至 9 月期间的钢铁进口主要来自中国，而这个南亚国家仍然是该合金的净进口国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-sept-steel-imports-led-by-china-govt-data-shows-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>东南亚为逃离特朗普对中国关税的工厂做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</link><description>该地区工业园区开发商表示，企业一直在将工厂从中国迁往东南亚，预计唐纳德·特朗普如果重新入主白宫，将对北京征收高额关税，随着他赢得大选，这一举措将加速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国派副总理出席巴库COP29气候峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</link><description>外交部发言人周五表示，中国副总理丁薛祥将于下周前往阿塞拜疆首都巴库出席第二十九届联合国气候变化框架公约(COP29)峰会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国公布1.4万亿美元地方债务计划但没有直接刺激</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-steps-tackle-hidden-debt-local-goverments-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国周五公布了10万亿元人民币（1.4万亿美元）的债务计划，以缓解地方政府融资压力并稳定疲软的经济增长，因为中国面临唐纳德·特朗普连任美国总统带来的新压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-steps-tackle-hidden-debt-local-goverments-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着欧盟碳关税的临近，新的绿色钢铁公司可能会获得回报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-green-steel-firms-could-reap-rewards-eu-carbon-tariffs-loom-2024-11-08/</link><description>在泰国东海岸，正在计划建造一座电弧炉，该电弧炉将向欧洲提供绿色钢铁，并受益于有争议的新规则，该规则将迫使买家支付高碳进口关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-green-steel-firms-could-reap-rewards-eu-carbon-tariffs-loom-2024-11-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>